sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Browser (Templates)
    participant View as Django View
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open Edit Note page
    UI->>View: GET /note/<id>/edit/
    View->>DB: SELECT Note WHERE id=<id>
    DB-->>View: Note
    View-->>UI: Render note_form.html

    User->>UI: Submit updated note
    UI->>View: POST /note/<id>/edit/ (title, content)
    View->>View: Validate NoteForm
    View->>DB: UPDATE Note SET title, content WHERE id=<id>
    DB-->>View: Updated
    View-->>UI: Redirect to /
    UI-->>User: Notes list updated
